Module AM25_myShelfie
Package it.polimi.ingsw.view.GUI

Class GraphicalUI

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
it.polimi.ingsw.view.GUI.GraphicalUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
SceneState, ViewInterface
public class GraphicalUI extends javafx.application.Application implements SceneState, ViewInterface
Main Class for GUI based on JavaFX, extends JavaFx's application, implements SceneState to handle SceneFactories and ViewInterface to receive messages forwarding from client connection.

      public void update()
      Description copied from interface: SceneState
      Method to cycle to next scenefactory, invoked from scene or SceneState itself. This method will call the next() method of the current instance of SceneFactory and will substitute the current factory with the result of the previous call of next(); then it will set the stage current scene with the result of the getter for the scene of the new factory
